{"type":"message","id":"2d7edc25","parentId":"dcc7efc0","timestamp":"2026-04-01T17:03:58.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only active session is this cron session itself - it's not a user conversation. There are no recent user messages in the last 5 minutes from actual users. The session shown is the cron job's own session. So there are no active user conversations. I should proceed with the autonomous learning task.\n\nLet me search for latest trends in enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services.","thinkingSignature":"00869345881ef967b3cb2c6a37d3135acff40ac802bbe98aaad7b02320591df2"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有 cron 会话本身活跃，没有真实用户对话。继续执行自主学习任务。\n"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":811,"output":145,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44937,"cost":{"input":0.00024329999999999998,"output":0.000174,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00173673}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775063033910}}
